abstract: National Assn of Realtors announces seasonally adjusted pending home sales index of 104.2 for month of January, up 1.7 percent from December 2014 figure, which was also revised higher; data indicates rebound in sales of existing homes in coming months.
lead_paragraph: The data points to a rebound in the sales of existing homes in the coming months, particularly as the spring buying season gets underway.

headline.main: Index of Pending Home Sales Rose in January
